reviewText: I really enjoyed this comedy dvd. It is good to know you can have comedy without all the cussing in it. I liked it more than Vol 1. I am looking forward to the next one.

If you love to laugh you will love to watch this daily....Should invite your friends or family and watch this together and
laugh....
Glad i ordered it.  There was no dull moment.  will share it with my women group at the church in our fellowship.
This DVD was very boring.  Volume 1 is much better. Do not waste your money or time with Volume 2.
